Dialogue: 11,0:21:03.89,0:21:08.90,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}Vibration, an undelivered emotion
Dialogue: 11,0:21:15.78,0:21:21.62,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}This place exists as a sequence of layers
Dialogue: 11,0:21:21.83,0:21:27.75,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}Of worlds recursing within worlds
Dialogue: 11,0:21:29.42,0:21:32.55,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}Although time is irreversible
Dialogue: 11,0:21:32.55,0:21:35.26,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}These sectors remain unaccessed
Dialogue: 11,0:21:35.26,0:21:37.30,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}Why did I receive this vision of a kiss
Dialogue: 11,0:21:37.30,0:21:40.26,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}Like a flash-forward?
Dialogue: 11,0:21:41.39,0:21:46.31,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}It came from so close—an outrageously large distance
Dialogue: 11,0:21:47.52,0:21:50.65,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}I can only conclude that our existence is defined by “0”s and “1”s
Dialogue: 11,0:21:50.65,0:21:53.99,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}In which I can be found right here
Dialogue: 11,0:21:54.86,0:21:58.28,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}I’ll tell you my feelings that I keep inside
Dialogue: 11,0:21:58.28,0:22:01.41,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}I remain in solitude, while in hold of
Dialogue: 11,0:22:01.41,0:22:07.17,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}A countless number of infinitely expansive universes
Dialogue: 11,0:22:07.17,0:22:10.59,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}That’s why I’ll make sure
Dialogue: 11,0:22:10.59,0:22:13.67,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}For the sake of your tomorrow
Dialogue: 11,0:22:13.67,0:22:19.47,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}That the blasphemy of the God ruling this universe
Dialogue: 11,0:22:19.84,0:22:22.93,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}Will never be repeated
