Dialogue: 30,0:00:02.92,0:00:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,For crying out loud...
Dialogue: 30,0:00:07.38,0:00:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for things settling down\Nafter the New Year’s thief fiasco...
Dialogue: 30,0:00:16.80,0:00:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a stickup, Maho!
Dialogue: 30,0:00:19.89,0:00:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is that?
Dialogue: 30,0:00:21.73,0:00:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You like it?
Dialogue: 30,0:00:23.02,0:00:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A hobby shop was selling these in Akihabara.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:25.90,0:00:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a toy gun for the festival.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:28.82,0:00:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You can shoot a bunch of beans with this thing.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:31.61,0:00:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,“Cast the demons out\Nand rake the bucks in!”, was it?
Dialogue: 30,0:00:35.78,0:00:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s “Bring the luck in!”, Professor.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:38.28,0:00:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, shouldn’t we be\Npreparing to go back home?
Dialogue: 30,0:00:41.66,0:00:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop buying junk we don’t need.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:44.00,0:00:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Reyes is gonna get mad.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:46.12,0:00:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose we did borrow this office...
Dialogue: 30,0:00:48.84,0:00:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We should leave it cleaner than we found it.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:51.55,0:00:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, we’ve got plenty\Nof time to pack things up.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:54.84,0:00:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But while we’re here,\Nwe oughta honor the festivals of Japan...
Dialogue: 30,0:00:58.85,0:01:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...and play around as is tradition!
Dialogue: 30,0:01:01.72,0:01:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven’t you heard the saying?
Dialogue: 30,0:01:03.56,0:01:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When the cat’s away, the mice will play.
Dialogue: 30,0:01:09.73,0:01:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Setsubun, huh?
Dialogue: 30,0:01:11.53,0:01:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s already that time of year...
Dialogue: 30,0:01:18.32,0:01:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Valentine’s, huh?
Dialogue: 30,0:02:52.00,0:02:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later, Boss. Take care.
Dialogue: 30,0:02:54.67,0:02:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 30,0:02:56.17,0:02:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Hold up.
Dialogue: 30,0:02:57.96,0:02:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 30,0:02:59.34,0:03:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Your payment for last month.
Dialogue: 30,0:03:01.47,0:03:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But I...
Dialogue: 30,0:03:03.60,0:03:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re protecting me, so I...
Dialogue: 30,0:03:06.56,0:03:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This and that are separate things.
Dialogue: 30,0:03:09.23,0:03:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 30,0:03:10.14,0:03:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take it.
Dialogue: 30,0:03:11.27,0:03:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 30,0:03:12.06,0:03:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Bet there’s not much in it anyways.
Dialogue: 30,0:03:14.73,0:03:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oho?
Dialogue: 30,0:03:16.53,0:03:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds to me like you’re\Nfine with working for free!
Dialogue: 30,0:03:19.24,0:03:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 30,0:03:20.45,0:03:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a bunch!
Dialogue: 30,0:03:21.91,0:03:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 30,0:03:24.03,0:03:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 30,0:03:30.71,0:03:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 30,0:03:35.46,0:03:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem happy today.
Dialogue: 30,0:03:37.96,0:03:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time getting paid for work.
Dialogue: 30,0:03:40.97,0:03:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you decided what you’ll use it on?
Dialogue: 30,0:03:43.72,0:03:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 30,0:03:45.01,0:03:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I still haven’t made up my mind yet...
Dialogue: 30,0:03:50.35,0:03:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This bakery has the tastiest cakes.
Dialogue: 30,0:03:53.02,0:03:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... N-No, it’s not like I...
Dialogue: 30,0:03:58.15,0:03:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s up, Kagari?
Dialogue: 30,0:03:59.73,0:04:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 30,0:04:01.03,0:04:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly is this about?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:05.32,0:04:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Valentine’s Day?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:07.12,0:04:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:08.29,0:04:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a special day where\Npeople convey their feelings...
Dialogue: 30,0:04:11.16,0:04:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...by giving chocolate to the ones they love.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:14.12,0:04:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To the ones they love...
Dialogue: 30,0:04:16.71,0:04:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when I was little...
Dialogue: 30,0:04:18.80,0:04:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...my mom used to search\Nfor ingredients to make us some.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:28.85,0:04:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How wonderful!
Dialogue: 30,0:04:31.60,0:04:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To put your feelings into\Na present for the ones you love!
Dialogue: 30,0:04:35.69,0:04:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s such a lovely tradition!
Dialogue: 30,0:04:38.65,0:04:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kagari?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:40.53,0:04:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, could it be that Kagari-san...
Dialogue: 30,0:04:43.49,0:04:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...has somebody in mind that she likes?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:47.03,0:04:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:49.78,0:04:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So? You’ll give him some, right?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:52.33,0:04:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you give it a rest already?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:54.58,0:04:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you it’s not happening.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But why not?!
Dialogue: 30,0:04:58.63,0:05:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re leaving soon, you know!
Dialogue: 30,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Convey your feelings before you go!
Dialogue: 30,0:05:03.67,0:05:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m telling you,\NOkabe-san isn’t like that to me!
Dialogue: 30,0:05:06.84,0:05:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep saying that and you’ll regret it.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:09.93,0:05:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Better to give and regret it than\Nto regret not giving anything at all.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:17.35,0:05:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:20.52,0:05:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:22.73,0:05:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:26.66,0:05:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s really nobody?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:30.37,0:05:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you already, there’s nobody!
Dialogue: 30,0:05:35.71,0:05:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, this is America...
Dialogue: 30,0:05:38.00,0:05:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s the guys who give valentines\Nto the girls they like here.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:41.96,0:05:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But, for a girl to share their\Nsecret feelings for someone...
Dialogue: 30,0:05:46.30,0:05:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t you think it’s romantic?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:48.51,0:05:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Romance is silly to a scientist.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:51.35,0:05:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,“To be a scientist is to be a true romantic.”
Dialogue: 30,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t you know the saying?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:56.43,0:05:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose quote is that?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:58.48,0:06:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s mine.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:00.86,0:06:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, what about you?
Dialogue: 30,0:06:03.86,0:06:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re a genius girl with\Ntheories begging to be published.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:07.82,0:06:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s a horde of men after you.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:15.20,0:06:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Several gentlemen have approached\Nme during my stay in America...
Dialogue: 30,0:06:20.21,0:06:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But after five or so minutes, they all run away.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:25.34,0:06:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic how they back down\Nafter losing an argument.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:29.18,0:06:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 30,0:06:31.14,0:06:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s already someone I have in mind.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:34.51,0:06:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re kidding!
Dialogue: 30,0:06:37.39,0:06:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways...
Dialogue: 30,0:06:38.52,0:06:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Better to give and regret it than\Nto regret not giving anything at all.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 30,0:06:46.65,0:06:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s the matter, spacing out like that?
Dialogue: 30,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s nothing.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:50.95,0:06:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, this conversation is over.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:53.37,0:06:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Eh?
Dialogue: 30,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t eh me. I’m powering off.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:56.70,0:06:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I overheard what you said there, nya.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 30,0:07:01.33,0:07:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To think Maho-nyan had that\Nsomeone special in her life, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 30,0:07:07.17,0:07:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your true feelings...\Npoured with love into chocolate!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:10.80,0:07:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Reach out... to her beloved!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:13.26,0:07:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now! Who were you listening to?!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I never said anything like that!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:17.89,0:07:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I possess the Eye of the sky God Horus!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:20.85,0:07:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see right through you, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:22.85,0:07:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I’m telling you...
Dialogue: 30,0:07:25.02,0:07:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolate...
Dialogue: 30,0:07:26.40,0:07:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 30,0:07:27.11,0:07:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 30,0:07:29.07,0:07:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nya, nya, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:33.99,0:07:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:34.99,0:07:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiryu-san?! H-How long have you been there?
Dialogue: 30,0:07:38.91,0:07:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole time.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:40.21,0:07:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So that whole conversation...
Dialogue: 30,0:07:43.04,0:07:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m giving... chocolate.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:45.59,0:07:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 30,0:07:46.84,0:07:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:48.34,0:07:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m giving chocolate.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:51.88,0:07:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:53.59,0:07:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you...
Dialogue: 30,0:07:55.26,0:07:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Moe-nyan has someone\Nshe wants to give chocolate to, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:08:00.93,0:08:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:02.19,0:08:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I never thought\NKiryu-san had someone like that...
Dialogue: 30,0:08:06.11,0:08:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it then?
Dialogue: 30,0:08:08.02,0:08:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Secret.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:09.19,0:08:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 30,0:08:13.82,0:08:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... This goes like... huh?
Dialogue: 30,0:08:17.24,0:08:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no... Not that way.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:19.83,0:08:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 30,0:08:22.62,0:08:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari has someone she likes...
Dialogue: 30,0:08:26.04,0:08:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m back!
Dialogue: 30,0:08:27.25,0:08:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Welcome home, Dad!
Dialogue: 30,0:08:29.84,0:08:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Nae! Have you been a good girl?
Dialogue: 30,0:08:32.67,0:08:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! I’m playing with Big Sis Kagari!
Dialogue: 30,0:08:36.09,0:08:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You are? That’s great!
Dialogue: 30,0:08:38.60,0:08:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guess what? Know what Big Sis did?
Dialogue: 30,0:08:41.60,0:08:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t! Nae-chan!
Dialogue: 30,0:08:43.18,0:08:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis is just so clumsy!
Dialogue: 30,0:08:45.98,0:08:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez! Why did you tell him that?!
Dialogue: 30,0:08:48.86,0:08:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because!
Dialogue: 30,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:52.65,0:08:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that well enough.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:54.61,0:08:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, not you too!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:00.45,0:09:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It can’t be...!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:02.79,0:09:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:04.21,0:09:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I think I love you!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:07.42,0:09:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can’t! No, you can’t!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:09.25,0:09:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to be Nae’s father before being a man!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:14.17,0:09:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I...
Dialogue: 30,0:09:16.47,0:09:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll be Nae-chan’s mother starting today!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:18.85,0:09:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:21.72,0:09:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No... There’s no way that’s happening...
Dialogue: 30,0:09:24.77,0:09:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s happening?
Dialogue: 30,0:09:25.85,0:09:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Uh, no! I...
Dialogue: 30,0:09:28.61,0:09:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,—Huh?\N—Talking to myself!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:30.61,0:09:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I think I’ll go clean up outside!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:33.65,0:09:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:35.28,0:09:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 30,0:09:36.32,0:09:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it’s just Okabe. What’s up?
Dialogue: 30,0:09:38.99,0:09:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Find a lead about the attackers or something?
Dialogue: 30,0:09:41.79,0:09:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that’s not why I came...
Dialogue: 30,0:09:44.54,0:09:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin-san!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:46.29,0:09:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you here today?
Dialogue: 30,0:09:48.67,0:09:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Came to see how it’s going.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:50.17,0:09:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? To check up on me?
Dialogue: 30,0:09:53.09,0:09:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... You seem good.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:55.34,0:09:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for going out of your way.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:58.22,0:09:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be cold.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:59.80,0:10:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I’m fine.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:01.72,0:10:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, I’ve got a message\Nfor you from Mayuri.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:05.35,0:10:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She said... Let’s pick out\Na phone for you together.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:09.15,0:10:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri-san said that?!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:11.15,0:10:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they talking about?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:13.82,0:10:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It can’t be...!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:15.74,0:10:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s so cold, and you...
Dialogue: 30,0:10:17.45,0:10:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m okay.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:18.78,0:10:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that, but... Your cheeks are so red.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:22.12,0:10:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheeks?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:25.79,0:10:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I’m so sorry!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:26.58,0:10:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,—Kagari... I-It’s okay...\N—They just... looked so cold!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:28.83,0:10:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s okay, Kagari...
Dialogue: 30,0:10:30.71,0:10:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:31.88,0:10:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything but that!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:33.42,0:10:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If it turns out like that, future\NBig Sis Mayu would hate me forever!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:38.47,0:10:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world should I do?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:42.93,0:10:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for all the help, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:45.35,0:10:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t mention it!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:46.64,0:10:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii and Faris-chan are good friends!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:49.23,0:10:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Any friend of Mayushii is a friend of ours!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:52.65,0:10:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear it!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:53.94,0:10:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, making costumes is fun!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:57.32,0:11:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, are you going handmade, Mayushii?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:00.36,0:11:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:01.36,0:11:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The customers will love it\Neven more with handmade costumes.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:05.58,0:11:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,C’mon! I’m not talking about the café costumes!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:08.79,0:11:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolate!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:10.00,0:11:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ll give some to Okarin-san, right?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Yeah!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:14.75,0:11:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mayushii isn’t very good at cooking though.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:18.46,0:11:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:19.80,0:11:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case... How’s this?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:23.18,0:11:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you please...
Dialogue: 30,0:11:25.05,0:11:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...eat Mayushii?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:26.18,0:11:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tutturu!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:28.39,0:11:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:30.98,0:11:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Fubuki-chan, you’re\Nsounding a lot like Daru-kun.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:34.56,0:11:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re kidding...
Dialogue: 30,0:11:36.15,0:11:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,—That’s the one thing...
Dialogue: 30,0:11:36.65,0:11:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,—But if you put your whole\Nheart into making them...\N—That’s the one thing...
Dialogue: 30,0:11:37.65,0:11:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,—But if you put your whole\Nheart into making them...\N—...I never wanted to hear...
Dialogue: 30,0:11:39.94,0:11:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,—...I’m sure Okarin-san will be incredibly happy.\N—...I never wanted to hear...
Dialogue: 30,0:11:43.03,0:11:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I don’t know...
Dialogue: 30,0:11:48.70,0:11:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Faris-san?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:51.37,0:11:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to Faris, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:06.51,0:12:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As of now, the 36th round table chocolate\Nmeeting will commence, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:11.85,0:12:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Round table...
Dialogue: 30,0:12:12.94,0:12:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...chocolate meeting?
Dialogue: 30,0:12:14.65,0:12:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, we’ll all be\Nmaking handmade chocolate!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:18.73,0:12:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible! You’ve done this 36 times!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:21.99,0:12:25.41,On Top,,0,0,0,,No... That’s too many if it’s once a year...
Dialogue: 30,0:12:23.40,0:12:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I know they told me to come,\Nbut what the heck am I doing here?
Dialogue: 30,0:12:25.41,0:12:28.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,And there’s no round table to be seen...
Dialogue: 30,0:12:28.33,0:12:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m curious about Kagari,\Nbut this is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:28.33,0:12:32.21,On Top,,0,0,0,,But still, that brings back memories!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:32.21,0:12:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m leaving.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:33.58,0:12:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure, nya?
Dialogue: 30,0:12:35.33,0:12:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave and no yummy chocolates\Nfor you to eat, nya.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:39.05,0:12:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,None of that matters to me.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:41.38,0:12:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-san is coming, nya.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:43.97,0:12:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I-If you insist!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:45.72,0:12:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, chocolate’s a good source\Nof energy in emergencies...
Dialogue: 30,0:12:49.51,0:12:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That settles it then!\NLet’s all get making chocolate, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:53.94,0:12:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:02.49,0:13:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Who are you giving chocolate to, Nae-chan?
Dialogue: 30,0:13:05.91,0:13:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:07.41,0:13:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Sure you’re not\Ngiving some to a guy in your class?
Dialogue: 30,0:13:12.00,0:13:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I’m not.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:14.50,0:13:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Big Sis Kagari?
Dialogue: 30,0:13:16.42,0:13:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? I’m...
Dialogue: 30,0:13:19.84,0:13:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a secret.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:20.84,0:13:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:21.84,0:13:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, no fair! Tell me!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s going well, nya.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:28.09,0:13:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If we hand out all these girls’ yummy\Nhandmade chocolate at the café...
Dialogue: 30,0:13:32.77,0:13:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It’ll be the best advertisement ever, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:37.73,0:13:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, nya?
Dialogue: 30,0:13:39.11,0:13:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh! Quiet or I’ll screw up!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:43.53,0:13:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Argh! Failed again!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:45.90,0:13:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You don’t have to be that precise...
Dialogue: 30,0:13:48.07,0:13:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Baking is a chemical reaction!\NIt’s an exact science!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:51.74,0:13:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ny-nyan!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:53.75,0:13:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Sniff, sniff...
Dialogue: 30,0:13:55.79,0:13:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Smells like smoke, nya.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:01.13,0:14:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:02.67,0:14:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why this happened?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:04.67,0:14:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop thinking and put it out! Hot, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:12.39,0:14:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what, nya?!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:14.47,0:14:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your microwave... broke.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:18.60,0:14:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can’t be putting foil in there, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:21.81,0:14:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nya?!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:22.65,0:14:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:23.73,0:14:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ny-a!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:24.90,0:14:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold up, everyone! Stop!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:27.40,0:14:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The recipe! Follow the recipe, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:30.78,0:14:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ny-a!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:36.66,0:14:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How strange...
Dialogue: 30,0:14:38.54,0:14:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,With this many girls, you’d expect someone\Nto know what they’re doing, nya...
Dialogue: 30,0:14:45.96,0:14:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 30,0:14:49.80,0:14:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for coming so late.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:52.85,0:14:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My saviors...
Dialogue: 30,0:14:55.68,0:14:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-nyan! Luka-nyan!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:58.68,0:15:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Faris-san?!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:01.19,0:15:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Here...
Dialogue: 30,0:15:02.98,0:15:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know if they came out well, but...
Dialogue: 30,0:15:05.94,0:15:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don’t you worry about that!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:08.61,0:15:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I guarantee they’re gonna taste good!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Daru.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:12.91,0:15:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hate to bug you in the middle of it, but...
Dialogue: 30,0:15:16.04,0:15:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you stop talking to\Nthe characters when you play?
Dialogue: 30,0:15:20.71,0:15:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry ’bout that.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:25.96,0:15:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s so peaceful...
Dialogue: 30,0:15:28.21,0:15:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If only it could last...
Dialogue: 30,0:15:30.59,0:15:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever...
Dialogue: 30,0:15:34.05,0:15:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:35.64,0:15:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see now! It’s the heat\Nof the water that melts it!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:39.93,0:15:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It’ll burn if you heat it directly.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:43.56,0:15:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we know!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:48.65,0:15:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Is this good?
Dialogue: 30,0:15:51.53,0:15:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you did a very good job.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:54.99,0:15:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:57.54,0:16:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like things are going smooth, nya.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:01.00,0:16:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor Faris is exhausted, nya...
Dialogue: 30,0:16:03.83,0:16:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, I’m sleepy, nya...
Dialogue: 30,0:16:07.80,0:16:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! I’m so sorry, Luka-kun!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:10.72,0:16:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It’s okay.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:12.13,0:16:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! If we don’t\Nwash your clothes, it’ll stain!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:17.35,0:16:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it’s all right.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:18.97,0:16:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it’s not. Oil has to be washed out quickly.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:22.44,0:16:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But I don’t have a change of clothes...
Dialogue: 30,0:16:26.65,0:16:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 30,0:16:28.15,0:16:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehhh?!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:32.78,0:16:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is incredible...
Dialogue: 30,0:16:35.32,0:16:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why do I have to...
Dialogue: 30,0:16:37.91,0:16:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...wear these clothes?
Dialogue: 30,0:16:40.75,0:16:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re just a replacement\Nuntil your clothes dry, but...
Dialogue: 30,0:16:44.46,0:16:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even us girls seem to be mesmerized...
Dialogue: 30,0:16:47.71,0:16:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis did this... to Big Bro?
Dialogue: 30,0:16:50.76,0:16:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 30,0:16:51.88,0:16:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Give me different clothes please!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:08.31,0:17:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 30,0:17:11.03,0:17:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Woohoo! They’re all done!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:14.07,0:17:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Think we did pretty good, yeah?
Dialogue: 30,0:17:17.99,0:17:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are we hanging onto these till Valentine’s?
Dialogue: 30,0:17:21.49,0:17:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s chocolate,\Nso it’ll last just fine in the fridge.
Dialogue: 30,0:17:25.62,0:17:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll write down the recipe for people\Nwho want to make their own, so feel free.
Dialogue: 30,0:17:31.50,0:17:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 30,0:17:32.42,0:17:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 30,0:17:33.71,0:17:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 30,0:17:37.30,0:17:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What’s wrong, Faris-san?
Dialogue: 30,0:17:41.39,0:17:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve burned out...
Dialogue: 30,0:17:43.60,0:17:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Into pure white...
Dialogue: 30,0:17:47.65,0:17:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Can’t have that, Big Sis!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:49.27,0:17:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nya?
Dialogue: 30,0:17:50.36,0:17:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The round table meeting doesn’t end\Ntill the messy kitchen is all cleaned up.
Dialogue: 30,0:17:54.61,0:17:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nya?
Dialogue: 30,0:17:57.82,0:18:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up! I’ll work you girls till you\Ncan eat peanuts through your belly button!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:03.08,0:18:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:04.41,0:18:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nae-sama, yes, Nae-sama!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:06.66,0:18:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t hear you!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:08.00,0:18:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me before stuffing\Nyour face with chocolate!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:10.88,0:18:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nae-sama, yes, Nae-sama!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:14.09,0:18:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nae-sama was something else...
Dialogue: 30,0:18:16.05,0:18:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Nae-sama... Nae-sama...
Dialogue: 30,0:18:19.72,0:18:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? For real?
Dialogue: 30,0:18:21.64,0:18:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari-tan and Okarin?
Dialogue: 30,0:18:23.47,0:18:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 30,0:18:24.89,0:18:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well that could be a disaster...
Dialogue: 30,0:18:27.64,0:18:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,With Kagari-tan being\NMayu-shi’s daughter and all...
Dialogue: 30,0:18:30.65,0:18:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom and daughter all to himself! I’m so jealous!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:33.52,0:18:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 30,0:18:34.90,0:18:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Well, joking aside...
Dialogue: 30,0:18:38.45,0:18:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari-tan from the future\Nand someone from the past...
Dialogue: 30,0:18:41.99,0:18:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...might have a high chance\Nof causing a paradox.
Dialogue: 30,0:18:46.25,0:18:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be... dangerous.
Dialogue: 30,0:18:50.12,0:18:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,—Hey, Kaga—\N—I’m so happy.
Dialogue: 30,0:18:52.54,0:18:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 30,0:18:53.59,0:18:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Making chocolate and\Nlaughing with everyone today...
Dialogue: 30,0:18:58.47,0:19:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t remember the past, but...
Dialogue: 30,0:19:01.14,0:19:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m happier now than I’ve ever been.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:03.93,0:19:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Or so I believe.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:06.10,0:19:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari-tan...
Dialogue: 30,0:19:10.69,0:19:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I really hope they like my chocolate...
Dialogue: 30,0:19:18.94,0:19:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll all be wearing\Nspecial costumes for you, Master!
Dialogue: 30,0:19:23.41,0:19:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s Valentine’s Day!
Dialogue: 30,0:19:26.20,0:19:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re doing a special service today!
Dialogue: 30,0:19:28.87,0:19:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Special handmade chocolates\Nbrought to you by MayQueen maids!
Dialogue: 30,0:19:33.46,0:19:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 30,0:19:36.21,0:19:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:37.13,0:19:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 30,0:19:38.84,0:19:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m so touched!
Dialogue: 30,0:19:43.01,0:19:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone’s loving it, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:19:48.35,0:19:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad this is only a one-time thing...
Dialogue: 30,0:19:51.39,0:19:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No way I’m going through\Nthat next year... Sniff, sniff...
Dialogue: 30,0:19:57.61,0:19:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 30,0:19:59.99,0:20:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if everyone gave out their chocolates?
Dialogue: 30,0:20:21.05,0:20:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,These were with the things Kagari left behind?
Dialogue: 30,0:20:24.64,0:20:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 30,0:20:25.80,0:20:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And not just for you two either...
Dialogue: 30,0:20:27.85,0:20:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She left one for me, my father,\Nand even the owner downstairs.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:32.06,0:20:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And to think... She was looking\Nforward to Valentine’s so much...
Dialogue: 30,0:20:36.40,0:20:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sure... she’ll come back to us, right?
Dialogue: 30,0:20:46.91,0:20:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I really hope they like my chocolate...
Dialogue: 30,0:20:56.13,0:20:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tastes pretty good.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:58.25,0:20:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummy...
Dialogue: 30,0:22:33.18,0:22:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And? You came back to America\Nwithout giving your chocolate?
Dialogue: 30,0:22:38.19,0:22:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 30,0:22:39.60,0:22:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, you had to fly back\Nbefore Valentine’s, but...
Dialogue: 30,0:22:42.36,0:22:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Could’ve mailed it or done it beforehand—
Dialogue: 30,0:22:44.36,0:22:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I did give it out.
Dialogue: 30,0:22:45.61,0:22:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 30,0:22:46.40,0:22:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,B-By giving it out,\Nyou mean your chocolate, right?
Dialogue: 30,0:22:49.91,0:22:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 30,0:22:51.16,0:22:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh, wait!
Dialogue: 30,0:22:53.33,0:22:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Were they happy with it?
Dialogue: 30,0:22:56.25,0:22:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno... I wonder...
Dialogue: 30,0:22:59.00,0:23:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a bit late handing it over...
Dialogue: 30,0:23:01.88,0:23:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Late?
Dialogue: 30,0:23:04.67,0:23:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Senpai!
Dialogue: 30,0:23:08.84,0:23:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 30,0:23:10.68,0:23:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems in Japan lately, people are\Ngiving their chocolate to special friends.
Dialogue: 30,0:23:15.89,0:23:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I... didn’t make any for you...
Dialogue: 30,0:23:18.68,0:23:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, there’s always next year.
Dialogue: 30,0:23:25.07,0:23:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
